#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.28"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.28:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Udāyivagga"
msgstr "3. With Udāyī"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 28. Nibbedhabhāgiyasutta → nibbedhasuttaṃ (bj) | nibbedho (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Nibbedhabhāgiyasutta"
msgstr "28. Helping Penetration"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.28:1.1"
msgid "“Nibbedhabhāgiyaṃ vo, bhikkhave, maggaṃ desessāmi;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you a path that helps penetration."

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.2"
msgid "taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.3"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, nibbedhabhāgiyo maggo?"
msgstr "And what is the path that helps penetration?"

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.4"
msgid "Yadidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.5"
msgid "satta bojjhaṅgā."
msgstr "It is the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.6"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.7"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo”ti."
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity.”"

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.8"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā udāyī bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Udāyī said to him:"

msgctxt "sn46.28:1.9"
msgid ""
"“kathaṃ bhāvitā nu kho, bhante, satta bojjhaṅgā kathaṃ bahulīkatā nibbedhāya "
"saṃvattantī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, how are the seven awakening factors developed and cultivated so as to "
"lead to penetration?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.88"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.28:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idha, udāyi, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ vipulaṃ mahaggataṃ "
"appamāṇaṃ abyāpajjaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Udāyī, it’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factor of mindfulness, "
"which relies on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripens as letting "
"go. And it is abundant, expansive, limitless, and free of ill will."

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.2"
msgid ""
"So satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvitena cittena anibbiddhapubbaṃ appadālitapubbaṃ "
"lobhakkhandhaṃ nibbijjhati padāleti;"
msgstr ""
"With a mind that has developed the awakening factor of mindfulness, they "
"penetrate and shatter the mass of greed,"

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.3"
msgid "anibbiddhapubbaṃ appadālitapubbaṃ dosakkhandhaṃ nibbijjhati padāleti;"
msgstr "the mass of hate,"

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.4"
msgid ""
"anibbiddhapubbaṃ appadālitapubbaṃ mohakkhandhaṃ nibbijjhati padāleti … pe …"
msgstr "and the mass of delusion for the first time. …"

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.5"
msgid ""
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ vipulaṃ mahaggataṃ appamāṇaṃ abyāpajjaṃ."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant develops the awakening factor of equanimity, which relies on "
"seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripens as letting go. And it is "
"abundant, expansive, limitless, and free of ill will."

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.6"
msgid ""
"So upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāvitena cittena anibbiddhapubbaṃ appadālitapubbaṃ "
"lobhakkhandhaṃ nibbijjhati padāleti;"
msgstr ""
"With a mind that has developed the awakening factor of equanimity, they "
"penetrate and shatter the mass of greed,"

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.7"
msgid "anibbiddhapubbaṃ appadālitapubbaṃ dosakkhandhaṃ nibbijjhati padāleti;"
msgstr "the mass of hate,"

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.8"
msgid "anibbiddhapubbaṃ appadālitapubbaṃ mohakkhandhaṃ nibbijjhati padāleti."
msgstr "and the mass of delusion for the first time."

msgctxt "sn46.28:2.9"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, udāyi, satta bojjhaṅgā evaṃ bahulīkatā nibbedhāya "
"saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is how are the seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated so "
"as to lead to penetration.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.28:2.10"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
